{
  "stem": "1641.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I've never seen anything like it, he said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he kept filming like mad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Says, look, I don't believe it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Look at all the dead bodies everywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the other soldiers came, and they emptied their pockets out, just throwing chewing gum at us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then they threw in chocolate bars, American Hershey chocolate bars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they had biscuits, chocolate biscuits.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then somebody brought some tinned corned beef, which was absolutely useless.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "First we couldn't open it, and if they could open it, and if you would eat it, you would die from it right away, anyhow.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was useless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The chocolate was pretty useless.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of the [INAUDIBLE] were good, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was very, very sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Very, very weak in all the excitement.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the next day, a fleet of-- of Red Cross ambulances arrived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But by that time, I was so weak-- I mean, even the previous weeks I was terribly weak.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I could hardly speak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just whisper.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I certainly couldn't stand up, and I couldn't even lift up my arm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I believe I was-- I was 32 kilograms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "From 72, I went down to 32.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was pretty low.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So-- anbd my big worry was that they would shove me in with the other dead, because everybody was dead around me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was about-- 20 bodies, I was the only one with some life in it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I thought that they would just push me in with the others and throw me up to the truck.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So if I pass out, then I'm just lying there, everybody dead, why check this one?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I was terribly worried.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So after the Americans came, and they kind of said, anybody alive here?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were looking for people who are still alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
